---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout 
	title="ELRS Mobile | Flash & Configure ExpressLRS from your Phone" 
	description="Flash and configure ExpressLRS receivers and transmitters directly from your iOS or Android device. 100% offline flashing, no PC or cables required."
>
	<main>
		<section class="hero">
			<h1 class="hero-gradient">The Field-Ready ExpressLRS Tool.<br/>No Laptop Required.</h1>
			<p>Flash V3.x and V4.x Firmware via Wi-Fi directly from your iOS or Android device.</p>
			
			<div class="cta-buttons">
				<a
					href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=io.datarx.elrsmobile"
					class="btn primary">Get it on Google Play</a
				>
				<a
					href="https://testflight.apple.com/join/jwU1WrpX"
					class="btn secondary">Join iOS TestFlight</a
				>
			</div>

			<div class="cta-secondary">
				<a href="/user_guide" class="secondary-link">Documentation</a>
				<span class="divider">|</span>
				<a
					href="https://github.com/wbhinton/ELRS-Mobile"
					class="secondary-link">Project GitHub</a
				>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="use-cases" class="use-cases">
			<div class="section-header">
				<h2>Why ELRS Mobile?</h2>
				<p class="section-sub">Real-world solutions for the field and the bench.</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="use-cases-grid">
				<div class="card use-case-card">
					<div class="card-header">
						<span class="badge">Problem</span>
						<h3>The "Dead Zone" Mismatch</h3>
					</div>
					<p>
						You're at a remote bando and realize your TX is on v4.0 but your RX is on v3.3. No cell service, no laptop, and no way to reach the Web Flasher.
					</p>
					<div class="solution">
						<strong>The Fix:</strong> Open the app, select your cached target, and flash via Wi-Fi. Back in the air in under 60 seconds—zero bars required.
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="card use-case-card">
					<div class="card-header">
						<span class="badge">Updates</span>
						<h3>Mass Configuration</h3>
					</div>
					<p>
						Changed your home Wi-Fi password or SSID? Bringing ten aircraft to your PC just to update a text string is a massive chore.
					</p>
					<div class="solution">
						<strong>The Fix:</strong> Bring your phone to the fleet. Connect to each quad's AP and update network settings or binding phrases natively and instantly.
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="features">
			<div class="card feature-card">
				<h3>⚡ Blazing Fast</h3>
				<p>Flash from local cache instead of waiting for web downloads or cloud compiles.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card feature-card">
				<h3>📡 Reliable Anywhere</h3>
				<p>Engineered for resilience. Direct OTA flashing ensures stable connections even in remote areas.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card feature-card">
				<h3>🛠 Unified Flow</h3>
				<p>One interface for all hardware. Automatically patches firmware with your config before flashing.</p>
			</div>
		</section>



		<section class="demo">
			<div class="section-header">
				<h2>See it in Action</h2>
				<p class="section-sub">Quick OTA flashing from local cache.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="video-container">
				<div class="phone-mockup">
					<iframe
						width="100%"
						height="100%"
						src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/v1gV7t4i-dA"
						title="ELRS Mobile Flashing Demo"
						frameborder="0"
						allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
						allowfullscreen
					>
					</iframe>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="installation">
			<div class="section-header">
				<h2>Get Started</h2>
				<p class="section-sub">Choose your platform and join the flight.</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="installation-type">
				<div class="store-grid">
					<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=io.datarx.elrsmobile" class="store-card">
						<div class="store-icon">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M17.523 15.3414L20.355 13.706C21.215 13.209 21.215 11.961 20.355 11.464L17.523 9.82944L14.771 12.5834L17.523 15.3414ZM13.883 13.4724L16.635 16.2234L5.656 22.564C5.071 22.902 4.331 22.795 3.865 22.28L13.883 13.4724ZM3.535 20.916L12.997 12.5844L3.535 4.25144C3.195 4.41444 3 4.76744 3 5.16644V20.0014C3 20.4 3.195 20.7534 3.535 20.916ZM13.883 11.6964L3.865 2.88844C4.331 2.37344 5.071 2.26644 5.656 2.60444L16.635 8.94544L13.883 11.6964Z"></path></svg>
						</div>
						<div class="store-info">
							<h3>Google Play</h3>
							<span class="badge">Production</span>
						</div>
					</a>
					<a href="https://testflight.apple.com/join/jwU1WrpX" class="store-card">
						<div class="store-icon">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M17.05 20.28c-.96.95-2.06 1.92-3.4 1.92s-1.8-.84-3.37-.84-2.1.84-3.41.84c-1.28 0-2.43-1.02-3.41-2.45-2.17-3.17-3.26-7.44-1.17-10.73 1-1.5 2.51-2.48 4.14-2.48 1.4 0 2.4 1.05 3.4 1.05s2.2-.9 3.55-.9c1.1 0 2.45.6 3.45 1.7-2.7 1.6-2.2 5.3 0 6.6-.7 1.8-1.7 3.6-2.94 5.16zM13 2c0 1.5-1.26 3.1-2.9 3.1-.15-1.9 1.4-3.5 2.9-3.5z"></path></svg>
						</div>
						<div class="store-info">
							<h3>TestFlight</h3>
							<span class="badge">iOS Beta</span>
						</div>
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="installation-advanced">
				<h3>Advanced Installation</h3>
				<p>Direct downloads and source code for power users.</p>
				<div class="advanced-links">
					<a href="https://github.com/wbhinton/ELRS-Mobile/releases" class="card advanced-card">
						<h4>Android APK</h4>
						<p>Sideload via GitHub Releases</p>
					</a>
					<a href="https://github.com/wbhinton/ELRS-Mobile" class="card advanced-card">
						<h4>Source Code</h4>
						<p>View on GitHub</p>
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="hardware">
			<div class="section-header">
				<h2>Compatibility</h2>
				<p class="section-sub">Broad support for the ExpressLRS ecosystem.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="hardware-grid">
				<div class="card hw-card">
					<h4>Supported Chipsets</h4>
					<ul>
						<li><strong>ESP8285</strong> (Common on RXs)</li>
						<li><strong>ESP32</strong> (Standard TX/RX)</li>
						<li><strong>ESP32-C3 / S3</strong> (Next-Gen)</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="card hw-card">
					<h4>Tested Hardware</h4>
					<ul>
						<li>RadioMaster XR1 / XR4 Dual Band</li>
						<li>BETAFPV SuperP / Micro TX</li>
						<li>HappyModel EP Dual / ES900</li>
						<li>RadioMaster Nomad / Pocket</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<div class="docs-link">
			<p>Need help? Visit the <a href="/user_guide">User Guide</a>.</p>
		</div>

		<footer>
			<p>&copy; 2026 Weston Hinton. Distributed under the GNU GPL v3.</p>
			<div class="trademark-notice">
				ExpressLRS™ is a trademark of ExpressLRS LLC. ELRS Mobile is an independent FOSS project and is not affiliated with or endorsed by ExpressLRS LLC.
			</div>
			<div class="support-notice">
				Support the project: <a href="https://opencollective.com/expresslrs/donate" class="support-link">Donate to ExpressLRS</a>
			</div>
		</footer>
	</main>
</Layout>

<script>
	document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
		const playStoreLinks = document.querySelectorAll('a[href*="play.google.com/store/apps/details"]');
		const testFlightLinks = document.querySelectorAll('a[href*="testflight.apple.com/join"]');

		playStoreLinks.forEach(link => {
			link.addEventListener('click', () => {
				if (typeof window.gtag === 'function') {
					window.gtag('event', 'app_store_click', {
						'app_store': 'Google Play',
						'event_category': 'App Install',
						'event_label': 'Play Store Link'
					});
				}
			});
		});

		testFlightLinks.forEach(link => {
			link.addEventListener('click', () => {
				if (typeof window.gtag === 'function') {
					window.gtag('event', 'app_store_click', {
						'app_store': 'TestFlight',
						'event_category': 'App Install',
						'event_label': 'TestFlight Link'
					});
				}
			});
		});
	});
</script>

<style>
	/* --- Design System --- */
	:root {
		--primary: #00bfa5;
		--surface: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
		--text: #ffffff;
		--text-muted: #a0a0a0;
		--background: #0a0a0a;
	}

	main {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 1.5rem;
	}

	section {
		padding: 5rem 0;
	}

	.section-header {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}

	h2 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}

	.section-sub {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.card {
		background: var(--surface);
		border-radius: 24px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(0, 191, 165, 0.1);
		padding: 2.5rem;
		transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
		height: 100%;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
	}

	.card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-8px);
		border-color: var(--primary);
		box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 191, 165, 0.1);
		background: rgba(0, 191, 165, 0.02);
	}

	/* --- Hero --- */
	.hero {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 8rem 0 5rem;
	}

	.hero-gradient {
		font-size: 4.5rem;
		font-weight: 900;
		line-height: 1.05;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #fff 30%, var(--primary));
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
	}

	.hero p {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto 3rem;
	}

	.cta-buttons {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.btn {
		padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
		border-radius: 14px;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		transition: all 0.2s;
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.btn.primary {
		background: var(--primary);
		color: #000;
	}

	.btn.secondary {
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		color: #fff;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
	}

	.btn:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		filter: brightness(1.1);
	}

	.cta-secondary {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 1rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.secondary-link {
		color: inherit;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}

	.secondary-link:hover {
		color: var(--primary);
	}

	/* --- Use Cases --- */
	.use-cases-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.card-header {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.badge {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
		border-radius: 100px;
		background: rgba(0, 191, 165, 0.1);
		color: var(--primary);
	}

	.use-case-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.use-case-card p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		flex-grow: 1;
	}

	.solution {
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background: rgba(0, 191, 165, 0.05);
		border-radius: 16px;
		border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
		font-size: 1rem;
	}

	.solution strong {
		display: block;
		color: var(--primary);
		margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
	}

	/* --- Features --- */
	.features {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.feature-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: var(--primary);
	}

	/* --- Demo --- */
	.video-container {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.phone-mockup {
		width: 320px;
		height: 640px;
		background: #000;
		border: 12px solid #1a1a1a;
		border-radius: 48px;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
		box-shadow: 0 40px 100px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
	}

	.phone-mockup::after {
		content: "";
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translateX(-50%);
		width: 140px;
		height: 28px;
		background: #1a1a1a;
		border-bottom-left-radius: 18px;
		border-bottom-right-radius: 18px;
	}

	/* --- Installation --- */
	.store-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.store-card {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background: var(--surface);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		border-radius: 20px;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: #fff;
		transition: all 0.2s;
	}

	.store-card:hover {
		border-color: var(--primary);
		background: rgba(0, 191, 165, 0.03);
		transform: translateY(-4px);
	}

	.store-icon svg {
		width: 48px;
		height: 48px;
		color: var(--primary);
	}

	.store-info h3 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
	}

	.installation-advanced {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 3rem;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
		border-radius: 32px;
		border: 1px dashed rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
	}

	.advanced-links {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	.advanced-card {
		padding: 1.5rem;
		text-align: left;
	}

	.advanced-card h4 {
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.advanced-card p {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	/* --- Hardware --- */
	.hardware-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.hardware-card h4 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
		color: var(--primary);
	}

	.hardware-card ul {
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
		list-style: none;
	}

	.hardware-card li {
		padding: 0.5rem 0;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	.hardware-card li:last-child {
		border: none;
	}

	.hardware-card li strong {
		color: #fff;
	}

	.note {
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-style: italic;
	}

	/* --- Footer --- */
	.docs-link {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 4rem 0;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
	}

	.docs-link a {
		color: var(--primary);
		font-weight: 700;
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	footer {
		text-align: center;
		padding-bottom: 5rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	.trademark-notice {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 2rem auto;
		line-height: 1.5;
		opacity: 0.6;
	}

	.support-notice {
		margin-top: 2rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background: rgba(0, 191, 165, 0.05);
		border-radius: 100px;
		display: inline-block;
	}

	.support-link {
		color: var(--primary);
		font-weight: 700;
		text-decoration: none;
		margin-left: 0.5rem;
	}

	/* --- Responsive --- */
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hero-gradient { font-size: 3rem; }
		h2 { font-size: 2.25rem; }
		section { padding: 4rem 0; }
		.card { padding: 1.5rem; }
	}
</style>
